1. **Content Automation (MoneyPrinterTurbo)**: Use LLMs to automate the entire video production pipeline. Strategy: Deploy "Viral content farms" for niche marketing.
2. **Autonomous BI (gpt-researcher)**: Implement deep research agents to monitor competitors and industry trends in real-time. Strategy: "AI-Driven Market Watch".
3. **Complex Orchestration (multi-agent-shogun)**: Build a "Digital Department" where multiple agents handle specific business functions (Sales, Support, Dev). Strategy: "Virtual HQ".
4. **Performance Coding (multi-agent-coding-system)**: Leverage top-tier coding agents to build and iterate on SaaS products rapidly. Strategy: "Rapid Prototype-to-Market".
